<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" class="h-100">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Codewars Statistics</title>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <link
      href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css"
      rel="stylesheet"
      integrity="sha384-1BmE4kWBq78iYhFldvKuhfTAU6auU8tT94WrHftjDbrCEXSU1oBoqyl2QvZ6jIW3"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="stylesheets/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="text-center text-white bg-dark h-100" cz-shortcut-listen="true">
    <div class="col col-md-9 d-flex h-100 flex-column mx-auto p-3">
      <header class="mb-auto">
        <div>
          <nav class="nav justify-content-between">
            <h3 class="float-md-start mb-0">Cover</h3>
            <a
              class="nav-link active"
              aria-current="page"
              href="https://codewars.com"
              target="_blank"
              >codewars.com</a
            >
          </nav>
        </div>
      </header>

      <main class="px-3">
        <h1 class="display-2">
          code<span class="text-info fw-bold">WARS</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="lead mb-5 mt-0">
          Quer descobrir suas estatísticas do codewars? Quais desafios
          completados, sua posição no rank geral, skills, clans, seu rank nas
          linguagens de programação?
        </p>
        <form action="/" method="post">
          <div class="input-group mb-3">
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control"
              name="user"
              id="user"
              placeholder="Username ou ID"
              aria-label="Username ou ID"
              aria-describedby="button-addon2"
            />
            <button
              class="btn btn-info fw-bold"
              type="submit"
              id="button-addon2"
            >
              Buscar
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </main>

      <footer class="mt-auto text-white-50">
        <p class="text-center text-mediumgray mb-0">
          © <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Codewars Statistics
        </p>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <!-- Bootstrap -->
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ka7Sk0Gln4gmtz2MlQnikT1wXgYsOg+OMhuP+IlRH9sENBO0LRn5q+8nbTov4+1p"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
  </body>
</html>
